<<<
 Derivation  for total kinetic energy in motion of electron in uniform electric field 
---

- $$ E_{f} = \frac{1}{2}m(v^{2} + \frac{eEx}{mv})^{2} $$
- $$ E_{f} = \frac{1}{2}m( \frac{ v^{4} + (eEx)^{2} }{m^{2}v^{2}} ) $$
- $$ E_{f} = \frac{1}{2}m( \frac{ v^{4} + (eEx)^{2} }{m^{2}v^{2}} ) $$
- $$ E_{f} = \frac{1}{2}\frac{v^{4}+ (eEx)^{2}}{mv^{2}} $$ 
   

